      "content": "i hear you, but it doesn't feel like a \"break\" is going to fix it. like, even if i sleep for a day, the same stuff is just waiting for me when i wake up. it's like a loop that never stops. everything feels so heavy and pointless... i honestly just feel like i've reached my limit and there's no way out of this cycle.",
